@startuml
autonumber
skinparam boxPadding 10
skinparam participantPadding 10

actor "Użytkownik" as User
participant "Frontend App\n(React)" as Front

box "Backend Application (Modular Monolith - Python)" #F0F4F8
    participant "API Module\n(FastAPI)" as API
    participant "YOLO Model\n(Inference)" as AI
    participant "Worker Module\n(Background Stitcher)" as Worker
end box

database "MongoDB\n(Shared State)" as Mongo
participant "MinIO \n(Blob Storage)" as S3

== 1. Inicjalizacja Sesji ==
User -> Front: Klik "Start Analizy"
Front -> API: POST /analysis/start\n(Auth Token)
activate API
API -> Mongo: Create Session\n{status: "RECORDING", frames: []}
Mongo --> API: session_id
API --> Front: { session_id: "xyz" }
deactivate API

== 2. Pętla Przetwarzania (Fake Streaming) ==
note right of Front
  Frontend wysyła klatki sekwencyjnie
  z wykorzystaniem backpressure (await)
end note

loop Dopóki trwa nagrywanie
    Front -> Front: Capture Frame (Canvas -> Blob)
    Front -> API: POST /frame/xyz (image/jpeg)
    activate API
   
    ' Równoległe działania API
    par Core Logic
        API -> AI: Detect Objects (Frame)
        AI --> API: BBox & Labels
    par and Persistence
        API -> S3: Upload Frame (frame_N.jpg)
        API -> Mongo: Atomic $push\n{s3_key: "...", order: N}
    end

    API --> Front: JSON Result { bbox: [...], label: "STOP" }
    deactivate API
   
    Front -> User: Rysuj ramkę na podglądzie (Live)
end

== 3. Finalizacja i Zlecenie Pracy ==
User -> Front: Klik "Zakończ"
Front -> API: POST /analysis/finish/xyz
activate API
API -> Mongo: Update Status\n{ status: "TO_PROCESS" }
API --> Front: 202 Accepted\n"Przetwarzanie wideo..."
deactivate API

== 4. Asynchroniczne Sklejanie (Worker) ==
note right of Worker
  Worker działa w osobnym wątku/procesie
  i odpytuje bazę (Polling)
end note

loop Co X sekund
    Worker -> Mongo: FindAndModify\n{status: "TO_PROCESS" -> "PROCESSING"}
    activate Worker
   
    opt Znaleziono sesję do przetworzenia
        Worker -> Mongo: Pobierz listę klatek (posortowaną)
        Mongo --> Worker: [key1, key2, key3...]
       
        Worker -> S3: Pobierz wszystkie obrazy (.jpg)
        Worker -> Worker: FFmpeg Stitching\n(JPEGs -> MP4)
       
        Worker -> S3: Upload finalnego wideo (.mp4)
        S3 --> Worker: video_url
       
        Worker -> Mongo: Update Session\n{status: "COMPLETED", url: "..."}
    end
    deactivate Worker
end

== 5. Wynik Końcowy ==
loop Polling (Frontend pyta o status)
    Front -> API: GET /analysis/status/xyz
    API -> Mongo: Check Status
    Mongo --> API: { status: "COMPLETED", videoUrl: "..." }
    API --> Front: Wynik gotowy
end

Front -> User: Wyświetl gotowe wideo z playera S3

@enduml